ABOUT THE SPEAKER
Stephen D. Lewis is a man who understands what it means to be saved by grace. That understanding is clearly seen in his passion for Christ and his love for people. 

Lewis is the featured speaker of the television and radio program, The Present Truth, which is nationally broadcast on several stations. His interest and aim is on winning and reviving personal commitments to a Saviour, Jesus, the Christ, "so that we can go home!”
